    {
      q: "Can EventHex handle large exhibitor counts at industrial expos?",
      a: "Yes. EventHex supports hundreds of exhibitors with booth allocation, floor plan management, and self-service portals where exhibitors manage their own profiles, product catalogs, and team members."
